{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":397,"text":"I'm here today to talk about social change,"},{"time":3957,"text":"not a new therapy or a new intervention"},{"time":7240,"text":"or a new way of working with kids\nor something like that,"},{"time":9957,"text":"but a new business model for social change,"},{"time":12902,"text":"a new way of tackling the problem."}]},{"cues":[{"time":15809,"text":"In Britain, 63 percent of all men"},{"time":19983,"text":"who come out of short sentences from prison"},{"time":23046,"text":"re-offend again within a year."},{"time":25567,"text":"Now how many previous offenses"},{"time":28185,"text":"do you think they have on average"},{"time":30568,"text":"managed to commit?"},{"time":33153,"text":"Forty-three."},{"time":35301,"text":"And how many previous times\ndo you think they've been in prison?"},{"time":38964,"text":"Seven."}]},{"cues":[{"time":40151,"text":"So we went to talk to the Ministry of Justice,"},{"time":42965,"text":"and we said to the Ministry of Justice,"},{"time":44853,"text":"what's it worth to you"},{"time":47205,"text":"if fewer of these guys re-offend?"},{"time":49382,"text":"It's got to be worth something, right?"},{"time":51551,"text":"I mean, there's prison costs,"},{"time":53378,"text":"there's police costs, there's court costs,"},{"time":56906,"text":"all these things that you're spending money on"},{"time":59638,"text":"to deal with these guys. What's it worth?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":62151,"text":"Now, of course, we care about the social value."},{"time":65146,"text":"Social Finance, the organization I helped set up,"},{"time":68432,"text":"cares about social stuff."},{"time":70675,"text":"But we wanted to make the economic case,"},{"time":73717,"text":"because if we could make the economic case,"},{"time":75495,"text":"then the value of doing this \nwould be completely compelling."},{"time":78516,"text":"And if we can agree on both a value"},{"time":81351,"text":"and a way of measuring whether we've been"},{"time":83688,"text":"successful at reducing that re-offending,"},{"time":86086,"text":"then we can do something"},{"time":88057,"text":"we think rather interesting."}]},{"cues":[{"time":90620,"text":"The idea is called the social impact bond."},{"time":94544,"text":"Now, the social impact bond is simply saying,"},{"time":96921,"text":"if we can get the government to agree,"},{"time":98560,"text":"that we can create a contract where"},{"time":101311,"text":"they only pay if it worked."},{"time":104770,"text":"So that means that they can try out new stuff"},{"time":107939,"text":"without the embarrassment"},{"time":109402,"text":"of having to pay if it didn't work,"},{"time":111410,"text":"which for still quite a lot of bits of government,"},{"time":113082,"text":"that's a serious issue."}]},{"cues":[{"time":114429,"text":"Now, many of you may have noticed"},{"time":116024,"text":"there's a problem at this point,"},{"time":117510,"text":"and that is that it takes a long time to measure"},{"time":119724,"text":"whether those outcomes have happened."},{"time":122490,"text":"So we have to raise some money."},{"time":125706,"text":"We use the contract to raise money"},{"time":128153,"text":"from socially motivated investors."},{"time":130377,"text":"Socially motivated investors:"},{"time":132731,"text":"there's an interesting idea, right?"},{"time":135029,"text":"But actually, there's a lot of people who,"},{"time":137420,"text":"if they're given the chance,"},{"time":138653,"text":"would love to invest in something"},{"time":140535,"text":"that does social good."},{"time":143298,"text":"And here's the opportunity."},{"time":145271,"text":"Do you want to also help government find"},{"time":147528,"text":"whether there's a better economic model,"},{"time":149964,"text":"not just leaving these guys to come out of prison"},{"time":152340,"text":"and waiting till they re-offend\nand putting them back in again,"},{"time":155211,"text":"but actually working with them"},{"time":156768,"text":"to move to a different path"},{"time":158327,"text":"to end up with fewer crimes"},{"time":160926,"text":"and fewer victims?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":162941,"text":"So we find some investors,"},{"time":165452,"text":"and they pay for a set of services,"},{"time":167822,"text":"and if those services are successful,"},{"time":170087,"text":"then they improve outcomes,"},{"time":172580,"text":"and with those measured reductions in re-offending,"},{"time":175221,"text":"government saves money,"},{"time":176296,"text":"and with those savings,"},{"time":177833,"text":"they can pay outcomes."},{"time":180287,"text":"And the investors do not just get their money back,"},{"time":182463,"text":"but they make a return."}]},{"cues":[{"time":184471,"text":"So in March 2010, we signed"},{"time":186912,"text":"the first social impact bond"},{"time":188932,"text":"with the Ministry of Justice"},{"time":190759,"text":"around Peterborough Prison."},{"time":192796,"text":"It was to work with 3,000 offenders"},{"time":195820,"text":"split into three cohorts of 1,000 each."},{"time":198748,"text":"Now, each of those cohorts"},{"time":200737,"text":"would get measured over the two years"},{"time":202568,"text":"that they were coming out of prison."},{"time":203770,"text":"They've got to have a year to commit their crimes,"},{"time":205825,"text":"six months to get through the court system,"},{"time":208370,"text":"and then they would be compared to a group"},{"time":210765,"text":"taken from the police national computer,"},{"time":212833,"text":"as similar as possible,"},{"time":214660,"text":"and we would get paid"},{"time":216194,"text":"providing we achieved a hurdle rate\nof 10-percent reduction,"},{"time":218983,"text":"for every conviction event that didn't happen."},{"time":222541,"text":"So we get paid for crimes saved."},{"time":226018,"text":"Now if we achieved that 10-percent reduction"},{"time":230122,"text":"across all three cohorts,"},{"time":231807,"text":"then the investors get a seven and a half percent"},{"time":234947,"text":"annualized return on their investment,"},{"time":237090,"text":"and if we do better than that,"},{"time":238630,"text":"they can get up to 13 percent"},{"time":240226,"text":"annualized return on their investment,"},{"time":242759,"text":"which is okay."}]},{"cues":[{"time":244877,"text":"So everyone wins here, right?"},{"time":248085,"text":"The Ministry of Justice can try out a new program"},{"time":250800,"text":"and they only pay if it works."},{"time":253243,"text":"Investors get two opportunities:"},{"time":255655,"text":"for the first time, they can invest in social change."},{"time":258711,"text":"Also, they make a reasonable return,"},{"time":260742,"text":"and they also know that"},{"time":262915,"text":"first investors in these kinds of things,"},{"time":265187,"text":"they're going to have to believers."},{"time":266844,"text":"They're going to have to care in the social program,"},{"time":268947,"text":"but if this builds a track record"},{"time":270939,"text":"over five or 10 years,"},{"time":272387,"text":"then you can widen that investor community"},{"time":274451,"text":"as more people have confidence in the product."},{"time":276907,"text":"The service providers, well, for the first time,"},{"time":279095,"text":"they've got an opportunity to provide services"},{"time":281954,"text":"and grow the evidence for what they're doing"},{"time":284181,"text":"in a really constructive way and learn"},{"time":286741,"text":"and demonstrate the value of what they're doing"},{"time":288563,"text":"over five or six years, not just one or two"},{"time":290582,"text":"as often happens at the moment."},{"time":292423,"text":"Society wins: fewer crimes, fewer victims."},{"time":295901,"text":"Now, the offenders, they also benefit."},{"time":298727,"text":"Instead of just coming out of the prison"},{"time":300157,"text":"with 46 pounds in their pocket,"},{"time":302081,"text":"half of them not knowing where they're spending"},{"time":303580,"text":"their first night out of jail,"},{"time":305718,"text":"actually, someone meets them in prison,"},{"time":308637,"text":"learns about their issues,"},{"time":310501,"text":"meets them at the gate,"},{"time":312420,"text":"takes them through to somewhere to stay,"},{"time":315173,"text":"connects them to benefits,\nconnects them to employment,"},{"time":317591,"text":"drug rehabilitation, mental health,"},{"time":319659,"text":"whatever's needed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":321389,"text":"So let's think of another example:"},{"time":324068,"text":"working with children in care."},{"time":325958,"text":"Social impact bonds work great"},{"time":327582,"text":"for any area where there is at the moment"},{"time":330243,"text":"very expensive provision that produces"},{"time":332642,"text":"poor outcomes for people."},{"time":334216,"text":"So children in the state care"},{"time":336130,"text":"tend to do very badly."},{"time":338565,"text":"Only 13 percent achieve a reasonable level"},{"time":342490,"text":"of five GCSEs at 16,"},{"time":345389,"text":"against 58 percent of the wider population."},{"time":347859,"text":"More troublingly, 27 percent of offenders in prison"},{"time":351518,"text":"have spent some time in care."},{"time":353559,"text":"And even more worryingly,"},{"time":354851,"text":"and this is a Home Office statistic,"},{"time":356823,"text":"70 percent of prostitutes"},{"time":358723,"text":"have spent some time in care."},{"time":360907,"text":"The state is not a great parent."},{"time":363907,"text":"But there are great programs"},{"time":366732,"text":"for adolescents who are on the edge of care,"},{"time":369744,"text":"and 30 percent of kids going into care"},{"time":371620,"text":"are adolescents."}]},{"cues":[{"time":373279,"text":"So we set up a program with Essex County Council"},{"time":376119,"text":"to test out intensive family therapeutic support"},{"time":379765,"text":"for those families with adolescents"},{"time":382805,"text":"on the edge of the care system."},{"time":384376,"text":"Essex only pays in the event"},{"time":387162,"text":"that it's saving them care costs."},{"time":389944,"text":"Investors have put in 3.1 million pounds."},{"time":392708,"text":"That program started last month."},{"time":394966,"text":"Others, around homelessness in London,"},{"time":397290,"text":"around youth and employment and education"},{"time":401170,"text":"elsewhere in the country."},{"time":402537,"text":"There are now 13 social impact bonds in Britain,"},{"time":405892,"text":"and amazing levels of interest in this idea"},{"time":408367,"text":"all over the world."},{"time":409890,"text":"So David Cameron's put 20 million pounds"},{"time":412605,"text":"into a social outcomes fund to support this idea."},{"time":415855,"text":"Obama has suggested 300 million dollars"},{"time":419035,"text":"in the U.S. budget for these kinds of ideas"},{"time":422568,"text":"and structures to move it forward,"},{"time":424254,"text":"and a lot of other countries"},{"time":425745,"text":"are demonstrating considerable interest."}]},{"cues":[{"time":427962,"text":"So what's caused this excitement?"},{"time":430018,"text":"Why is this so different for people?"},{"time":432537,"text":"Well, the first piece, which we've talked about,"},{"time":435029,"text":"is innovation."},{"time":436247,"text":"It enables testing of new ideas"},{"time":439445,"text":"in a way that's less difficult for everybody."}]},{"cues":[{"time":443038,"text":"The second piece it brings is rigor."},{"time":445674,"text":"By working to outcomes, people really have to test"},{"time":448967,"text":"and bring data into the situation\nthat one's dealing with."},{"time":452845,"text":"So taking Peterborough as an example,"},{"time":455338,"text":"we add case management"},{"time":457561,"text":"across all of the different organizations\nthat we're working with"},{"time":460217,"text":"so they know"},{"time":461502,"text":"what actually has been done with different prisoners,"},{"time":463651,"text":"and at the same time they learn"},{"time":465720,"text":"from the Ministry of Justice, and we learn,"},{"time":468146,"text":"because we pushed for the data,"},{"time":469881,"text":"what actually happens, whether\nthey get re-arrested or not."},{"time":472088,"text":"And we learn and adapt the program accordingly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":475376,"text":"And this leads to the third element, which is new,"},{"time":478313,"text":"and that's flexibility."},{"time":480415,"text":"Because normal contracting for things,"},{"time":483528,"text":"when you're spending government money,"},{"time":485589,"text":"you're spending our money, tax money,"},{"time":488100,"text":"and the people who are in charge \nof that are very aware of it"},{"time":490797,"text":"so the temptation is to control\nexactly how you spend it."},{"time":494647,"text":"Now any entrepreneur in the room knows"},{"time":497700,"text":"that version 1.0, the business plan,"},{"time":499797,"text":"is not the one that generally works."},{"time":502644,"text":"So when you're trying to do something like this,"},{"time":504947,"text":"you need the flexibility to adapt the program."},{"time":507640,"text":"And again, in Peterborough, we started off"},{"time":510352,"text":"with a program, but we also collected data,"},{"time":514509,"text":"and over the period of time,"},{"time":516386,"text":"we nuanced and changed that program"},{"time":518584,"text":"to add a range of other elements,"},{"time":521204,"text":"so that the service adapts"},{"time":522969,"text":"and we meet the needs of the long term"},{"time":525470,"text":"as well as the short term:"},{"time":527534,"text":"greater engagement from the prisoners,"},{"time":530643,"text":"longer-term engagement as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":533422,"text":"The last element is partnership."},{"time":535958,"text":"There is, at the moment, a stale \ndebate going on very often:"},{"time":539135,"text":"state's better, public sector's better,"},{"time":541260,"text":"private sector's better, social sector's better,"},{"time":544771,"text":"for a lot of these programs."},{"time":546439,"text":"Actually, for creating social change,"},{"time":548421,"text":"we need to bring in the expertise"},{"time":550160,"text":"from all of those parties"},{"time":551856,"text":"in order to make this work."},{"time":553444,"text":"And this creates a structure"},{"time":555487,"text":"through which they can combine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":557462,"text":"So where does this leave us?"},{"time":559394,"text":"This leaves us with a way"},{"time":561228,"text":"that people can invest in social change."},{"time":564215,"text":"We've met thousands, possibly millions of people,"},{"time":567202,"text":"who want the opportunity to invest in social change."},{"time":569635,"text":"We've met champions all over the public sector"},{"time":572724,"text":"keen to make these kinds of differences."},{"time":575139,"text":"With this kind of model,"},{"time":576924,"text":"we can help bring them together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":578860,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":580822,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}